Hi Logan - when I load the page or click the menu links, the menu isn't shrunk, but it is changing locations. Initially it loads on the left next to the logo and then it moves to the permanent spot near the middle. It happens very quickly, just a flash, but I believe this is caused by how you have the position configured.

When I uncheck this from the dev console, the menu moves back to the initial position:

```.cst-hder-grp .row .cst-header-menu {
    width: 50%;
}```
